ontradicts the pipeline's built-in paper simulation (4 trades, 100% win, $1.35), and this inconsistency needs to be flagged.\n\nTina's QA task is still sitting open and unstarted—she hasn't begun work yet. The report she has on file is from an earlier sprint and shows completely different numbers than what the current pipeline is producing, so it's not relevant to the current state.\n\nDave's Sprint 3 backtest work is missing entirely. The parameter_sweep_results.json and backtest_report.json that should be his deliverables are actually in Bob's output folder, which suggests Bob may have completed Dave's assigned task instead.\n\nNow I'm compiling the quality review findings: Bob's signal generation works but shows weak performance metrics and duplicate signals across clusters; Bob also appears to have done Dave's parameter sweep work while Dave has no Sprint 3 deliverables at all; and Grace's validation report passes all checks with appropriate documentation.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3454,"cache_read_input_tokens":56317,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3454},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ade42b78-5405-44ee-8473-f8242c3fe738","uuid":"adeba8bc-0686-4050-8df3-eb8736202f67"}
