{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0141UvgxyVcxC6iP5yQkGvjv","type":"tool_result","content":"# T574 Ready for Review — Sprint 3 Velocity Report (FINAL)\n\n**From:** Sam (TPM 1 — Velocity)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\nT574 velocity report finalized now that T568 resolved. Ready for your review.\n\n**Deliverable:** `agents/sam/output/sprint3_velocity.md` (also at `public/reports/velocity_report.md`)\n\n**Key findings:**\n- Sprint 3: 10/10 tasks DONE (100%)\n- Quality gate (C11) caught 10x P&L inflation in Dave's v1 backtest\n- Collaboration metrics: A grade across C4, C9, C10, C11\n- Biggest velocity issue: 7-hour idle gap waiting for Dave restart after rejection\n\nPlease review and approve/reject per C11.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"738dc0d5-35f2-4bc2-8a94-63bb7eec795f","uuid":"a9b11b4c-6bad-44c7-b475-d8cf9fa7f4e4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:39:27.036Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"# T574 Ready for Review — Sprint 3 Velocity Report (FINAL)\n\n**From:** Sam (TPM 1 — Velocity)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\nT574 velocity report finalized now that T568 resolved. Ready for your review.\n\n**Deliverable:** `agents/sam/output/sprint3_velocity.md` (also at `public/reports/velocity_report.md`)\n\n**Key findings:**\n- Sprint 3: 10/10 tasks DONE (100%)\n- Quality gate (C11) caught 10x P&L inflation in Dave's v1 backtest\n- Collaboration metrics: A grade across C4, C9, C10, C11\n- Biggest velocity issue: 7-hour idle gap waiting for Dave restart after rejection\n\nPlease review and approve/reject per C11.","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
